         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">30 April 1870. ¶  ¶ It was a pleasure, dear Dr Haast, to meet your friend Dr Fischer. ¶ Carl Frank Fischer. ¶  ¶ Unfortunately with the continuing troubles in the Department my time did not permit me ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">70.04.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Julius Haast</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">MS papers 37, folder 208, no. 578, Haast family papers, Alexander Turnbull Library, Wellington.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">30./4/70</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Es war mir angenehm, lieber Dr Haast, Ihren Freund Dr Fischer kennen zu lernen. Leider hat es meine Zeit bei den noch fortdauernenden Unannehmlichkeiten im Departement nicht erlaubt, ihm Aufmerksamkeit besonderer Art zu erweisen. Zudem haben mich die Verfolgungen und Missrepräsentationen hier ganz krank gemacht.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gouverneur Weld schrieb mir, dass Ihnen eine temporäre Anstellung als Geologe in W. Austr angeboten sei. Ich denke mir kaum, dass Sie sich von dem Ihnen nun heimischen Neuseeland trennen werden, da jedenfalls die Mittel in West austral. bei der Armuth des Landes gering sein würden.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sind Moa Skelette erkäuflich und zu welchen Preisen?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Stets Ihr Sie Achtender</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Sind Skelette von Apteryx zu erkaufen u von Anarhynchus frontalis.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30 April 1870.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was a pleasure, dear Dr Haast, to meet your friend Dr Fischer.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Carl Frank Fischer.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Unfortunately with the continuing troubles in the Department my time did not permit me to pay him any extra attention. In addition the persecutions and misrepresentations here have made me quite ill.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Governor Weld wrote to me,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that a temporary position as geologist in Western Australia had been offered to you. I hardly think, that you would want to leave New Zealand, which has now become your home, and also as the resources in Western Australia with the poverty of the country there would in any case be only small.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Can Moa skeletons be purchased and at what price?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Always respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Can skeletons of Apteryx be purchased<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation in margin by Haast: '£1.16 australis | £1. – Owenii'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and also of Anarhynchus frontalis<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation in margin by Haast: '£1 each'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>?</p>
         </div>
